title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\ContainerRegistryDestination
name: ContainerRegistryDestination
description:
The Container Registry location for the container image.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.ContainerRegistryDestination

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.output_uri
params.description: Required. Container Registry URI of a container image. Only Google Container Registry and Artifact Registry are supported now. Accepted forms: Google Container Registry path. For example: gcr.io/projectId/imageName:tag. Artifact Registry path. For example: us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/projectId/repoName/imageName:tag. If a tag is not specified, "latest" will be used as the default tag.
